snippet.textDisplay: Watched Day 0 today and did Day 1 with it too. I usually don't do practices longer than around 30 minutes but once I got into it I felt great! Hoping these 30 days will help me reset my productivity because it definitely took a hit during the holiday season haha. Thank you so much for these videos, they really help me slow down and be more present with myself.

snippet.textDisplay: Last year, I embarked on this 30-day journey at a time when I was very depressed and vulnerable. I somehow managed to stick to it till the very end and I'd like to think it kick started a huge year of achievement for me. You have no idea how excited I was to get started this time around!! Or how incredible it felt to look back on the progress I've made in the last year. Thank you, dear Adriene ❤️ from the bottom of my heart
